<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal" tal:omit-tag="textual">
<head tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <title tal:omit-tag="textual">Registration to <span tal:replace="site_name"></span></title>
</head>
<body tal:omit-tag="textual">

    <h1 tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for starting your registration to the platform <span tal:replace="site_name"></span></h1>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">To verify your email address and ensure you're a human (not a robot), we've devised a series of simple calculations. Please solve the four calculations labeled from A to D and enter the respective results in the corresponding fields on the registration page linked below.</p>
    <div omit-tag="textual">

        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Operation A is <span tal:content="challenge_A" tal:omit-tag="textual">The first challenge</span></p>
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Operation B is <span tal:content="challenge_B" tal:omit-tag="textual">The second challenge</span></p>
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Operation C is <span tal:content="challenge_C" tal:omit-tag="textual">The third challenge</span></p>
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Operation D is <span tal:content="challenge_D" tal:omit-tag="textual">The fours challenge</span></p>
    </div>
    <a tal:attributes="href string:${page_register_whith_oid}" tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <span tal:replace="string:${page_register_whith_oid}"></span>
    </a>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for your interest in our activities. We look forward to welcoming you soon!</p>
    
    <footer tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Sincerely,</p>
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">The team at <span tal:replace="site_name">Site</span></p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>